Added `SOA_SERIAL_AUTO_INCREMENT` constance configuration option to automatically increment SOA serial numbers when zone data changes.
Added `increment_soa_serial()` method to `DNSZone` model with atomic row-level locking.
Added `post_save` and `post_delete` signal handlers for all DNS record types to trigger serial increment.
Added explicit `soa_serial` range validation (0–2,147,483,647) on `DNSZoneForm` and `DNSZoneSerializer`.
